Detailed Description

cvmx_pci_win_wr_data

PCI_WIN_WR_DATA = PCI Window Write Data Register

Contains the data to write to the address located in the PCI_WIN_WR_ADDR Register. Writing the least-significant-byte of this register will cause a write operation to take place.
